data.title: LDVIC Account Creation Student Accounts
data.meta_description: LDVIC__Account_Creation_Student_Accounts - Free download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document contains information about the creation of GENYO accounts for students of Liceo de Victoria in Victoria, Laguna, Philippines. It includes the names of 265 students along with their assigned usernames. The usernames follow a pattern of LDVIC plus a 4-digit number. It also includes information about the school name, location, and the creation of GENYO accounts for students grouped by their level, section, and assigned password.
